    "Frame consistency, frame quality, and relevant information are some common criteria for selecting frames for deepfake detection.",
    "Use a more realistic number of input frames to increase performance.",
    "There are more parameters the more frames that are entered.",
    "Furthermore, two frames are not taken into account since the 3D model may not be properly utilized in the time dimension with two frames.",
